The news comes just two months after Minnie announced her resignation from SABC's SoccerZone, which she co-presented for four years. In a statement released over the weekend, Minnie could not hide her excitement. "Sport is part of my DNA. I couldn't be happier right now than to be part of such an incredible leading international brand like SuperSport. Exciting times ahead," she said. Minnie is set to work on shows including Love PSL and Super Diski presentation, and is set to host a brand new lifestyle show on Mzansi Magic. The announcement was made at a swanky party on Saturday night. Tonight was amazing Thank you to my amazing team #psl10yearcelebration pic.twitter.com/gJK1m4gQr3